.claude/tmp/

# Claude Design handoff bundle (local only)
.design-bundle/

# Graphify — local/ephemeral build artifacts (graph.json, graph.html, GRAPH_REPORT.md, manifest.json are committed)
graphify-out/cache/
graphify-out/.graphify_*
graphify-out/cost.json
graphify-out/*-callflow.html
graphify-out/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-*/
